{"tid":1239041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行紅海讓路 免費送湯震撼日本 日本人：果然香港不是中國","createTime":"2019-06-18T04:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T05:47:06.000Z","uid":57898,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e76f4c1f4fe9afca1800bcee2f7ce97fe3323b25","tid":1239041,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:40:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2379198/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E7%B4%85%E6%B5%B7%E8%AE%93%E8%B7%AF%20%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E9%80%81%E6%B9%AF%E9%9C%87%E6%92%BC%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%20%E8%AD%9A%E5%B0%8F%E7%92%B0%E6%84%9F%E5%8B%95%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%BC%E5%BE%97%E9%A9%95%E5%82%B2%E5%98%85%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2379198%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%25AE%2593%25E8%25B7%25AF%2520%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E9%2580%2581%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E9%259C%2587%25E6%2592%25BC%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%2520%25E8%25AD%259A%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2580%25BC%25E5%25BE%2597%25E9%25A9%2595%25E5%2582%25B2%25E5%2598%2585%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=6b600675\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2379198/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E7%B4%85%E6%B5%B7%E8%AE%93%E8%B7%AF%20%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E9%80%81%E6%B9%AF%E9%9C%87%E6%92%BC%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%20%E8%AD%9A%E5%B0%8F%E7%92%B0%E6%84%9F%E5%8B%95%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%BC%E5%BE%97%E9%A9%95%E5%82%B2%E5%98%85%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Jy6Sf5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Jy6Sf5.png&h=a8a10779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚日本新聞報導遊行事件，引來日本網民瘋狂討論。事關遊行當日明明人山人海，擠個水洩不通，但每次有救護車要經過，人潮都會自動分隔兩邊讓路，等待救護車駛走又再重新集合，猶如摩西分紅海一樣，相當壯觀。日本網民激讚香港人公民質素，對於此等有系統的群眾秩序自愧不如，不但留言高達過千個，片段也登上Twitter日本熱門首位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FmcNO3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7FmcNO3.png&h=0e812e40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2U60WHo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2U60WHo.png&h=9209ee7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n藝人響應遊行為高質港人感動 唯唯「幫手」登上外國新聞<br />\n<br />\n除了王喜、何韻詩、王宗堯、朱薰有參加今次遊行，譚小環都有同老公去，仲為遊行人士的好市民表現表示感動：「好多香港良心，好感動。我從未見過暴徒會咁有禮貌，咁有秩序。香港，仲係有好多值得驕傲既香港。」，又話：「有人話今日有200萬人，我絕對相信！為要林鄭下台，香港人可以去到幾盡？自己睇，全世界都睇到。香港人，我愛你。」除此之外，影帝黃秋生也有分享影片：「而家全世界都知香港喺邊度」。<br />\n<br />\n另外唯唯梁競徽最近被網民多次改圖成為「反送中人士」，在網上人氣極高，雖然他早就在微博公開澄清自己沒有參加遊行，不過一眾網民一於少理，繼續封他為「人民英雄」，甚至將他的頭像印成海報，周圍貼到街上。昨晚一間會在全球播放的歐洲新聞台Euronews報道遊行時，竟然將遊行人士高舉梁競徽惡搞海報的場面都拍下，令網民又驚又喜，紛紛為梁競徽的間接上鏡感到興奮，又多謝他為香港人「付出」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9ERiWd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9ERiWd.png&h=5e6f3c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uctZsPy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuctZsPy.png&h=94b81d03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唯唯人民英雄</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977d4a7e069d09e1692dc7ccf4d12b428b1fad77","tid":1239041,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"